=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755525&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8yHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=05dfecbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755525&h=66b84008\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190825/20755525</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zFiXAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zFiXAR.png&h=62deb993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The Amazon is burning because the world eats so much meat</span><br />\nBy Eliza Mackintosh, CNN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2019/08/23/americas/brazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2Famericas%2Fbrazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl%2Findex.html&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8yHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=82f2081d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2Famericas%2Fbrazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl%2Findex.html&h=216c3621\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2019/08/23/americas/brazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當大家打緊國際輸出革命，全球各國都幫緊香港人發聲既時候，另一單近期最大既新聞就係亞馬遜森林火燭，而香港竟然係入口最多牛肉既地方？？？<br />\n<br />\n唔該，依家香港軟實力啱啱先建立到，出國同人講自己係香港人，人地都會知你係民主鬥士，你唔會想又加返條破壞環境既罪名呀嘛？ 就算無人怪香港人，依個都係再次展現香港人人性光輝既重要機會！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">即刻發起戒食牛肉行動！！！！<br />\n以示香港人面向國際，對國際社會既責任感！！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=