f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbd0bbe57dac90dcba0447051fa7946be5dce4d","tid":1505944,"uid":268120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"入哂劇本<br />\n繼續自編自導自演<br />\n不過仲未夠膽講示威者係恐怖分子<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰晚上到瑪嘉烈醫院探望荃灣執勤受傷警員<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰晚上到瑪嘉烈醫院，探望較早時在荃灣執勤受傷的多名警員。警方在社交網站專頁表示，盧偉聰對於妄顧他人安全的非法暴力行為，感到非常憤怒，予以強烈譴責，對警員受到嚴重傷害感到非常難過。警方又說，針對任何暴動行為，引致他人身體嚴重受傷，甚至威脅人命，警隊必定全力追究。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-26 00:09:52"},{"pid":"26e7f37f161f3208497ade27918e5896ceed5aca","tid":1505944,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"acd7e429e5eda5427933ef95c06d8aa655fe47d6","tid":1505944,"uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"f7eacb2cd130df40d0a2f6709a9245d10d360de8","tid":1505944,"uid":268120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"放水，自己人，走得<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/7wpfs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F7wpfs&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp8yHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=377196f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/7wpfs</a>"},{"pid":"2f8e367ac27e668e52ec0e07224d8e9d965a5d01","tid":1505944,"uid":79228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:52:44.000Z","msg":"小心提防就夠，唔好捉鬼，可能係自己友組咗隊"},{"pid":"ad4662b9f2d28b99020335fa636b5fbc7059d950","tid":1505944,"uid":268120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f8e367ac27e668e52ec0e07224d8e9d965a5d01","tid":1505944,"uid":79228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:52:44.000Z","msg":"小心提防就夠，唔好捉鬼，可能係自己友組咗隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:53:44.000Z","msg":"希望係<br />\n<br />\n但要提防<br />\n<br />\n下次自己試吓痴塊粉紅色落